metadata.name: 「恋病」koiyamai / lovesick
metadata.description:
“WHY IS SHE MESSING WITH MY HEAD?!  
My blood boils just to picture her face! 
There is only one way to get her out of mine, I am going to get this bitch vanished!”

Tomoki's life changes 180 degrees when Arthropoda Arachnids: White Crab Spider bites her. Within seconds her body was taken over by Arachnids DNA. The bite brought Tomoki’s hidden side within her, that she, herself has was never aware of. Her common sense is no longer hers. The “innocent” Tomoki-chan is now a vengeful little woman, taken over by wrath and envy. She preys her enemy down in silence, slowly with a highly poisonous attacks.
